<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>ONG - Novo Caminho</title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "tailwind", "inter-font", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Caprasimo&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>

  <body class="bg-white">
    <%= render 'shared/site-navbar' %>
    <div class="container mx-auto p-12 md:p-32">
      <div class="mb-8 md:mb-0">
        <%= link_to 'Voltar', sites_path, class: "rounded-full py-6 px-2.5 font-bold bg-black text-white" %>
      </div>
      <section class="text-center lg:text-left">
        <div class=" md:px-6 md:px-12">
          <div class="container mx-auto xl:px-32">
            <div class="flex grid items-center lg:grid-cols-2">
              <div class="mb-12 md:mt-12 lg:mt-0 lg:mb-0">
                <div
                  class="relative z-[1] block rounded-lg bg-[hsla(0,0%,100%,0.55)] px-6 py-12 shadow-[0_2px_15px_-3px_rgba(0,0,0,0.07),0_10px_20px_-2px_rgba(0,0,0,0.04)] backdrop-blur-[25px] dark:shadow-black/20 md:px-12 lg:-mr-14">
                  <h2 class="mb-2 text-3xl font-bold text-primary">
                    <%= @animal.name %>
                  </h2>
                  <p class="mb-4 font-semibold"><%= @animal.race %></p>
                  <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-500">
                    <%= @animal.description %>
                  </p>
                  <p class="mb-6 text-neutral-500">
                    Ad, at blanditiis quaerat laborum officia incidunt
                    cupiditate dignissimos voluptates eius aliquid minus
                    praesentium! Perferendis et totam ipsum ex aut earum libero
                    accusamus voluptas quod numquam saepe, consequuntur nihil
                    quia tenetur consequatur. Quis, explicabo deserunt quasi
                    assumenda ea maiores nulla, et dolor saepe praesentium natus
                    error reiciendis voluptas iste. Esse, laudantium ipsum
                    animi, quos voluptatibus atque vero repellat sit eligendi
                    autem maiores quasi cum aperiam. Aperiam rerum culpa
                    accusantium, ducimus deserunt aliquid alias vitae quasi
                    corporis placeat vel maiores explicabo commodi!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="md:mb-12 lg:mb-0">
                <% if @animal.photo.present? %>
                  <% ActiveStorage::Current.url_options = { host: request.base_url } %>
                  <%= image_tag @animal.photo.url, class: "lg:rotate-[6deg] w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:shadow-black/20" %>
                <% else %>
                  <%= image_tag("cachorro-sem-foto.png", class: "lg:rotate-[6deg] w-full rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:shadow-black/20") %>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
 </body>
</html>
